      • addNeighbor

        public void addNeighbor(Edge e)
        Add a directly connected synaptic neighbor to this Node's existing Edges. Note that since this is an UndirectedNode, no distinction is made between dendrites (inputs) and axons (outputs).
        Parameters:
        e - the synaptic Edge to add.
